title: Ryan Adams - Live Acoustic 2000-02-14 - Seattle, WA
description:
Ryan Adams
Tractor Tavern
Seattle, WA
2000-02-14


Wonderful soundboard recording of an acoustic concert Ryan Adams played together with Kim Richey & Chuck Prophet. Torrent includes Memories Of You and Dancing With The Women At The Bar from 2000-02-13 as filler after Come Pick Me Up, since it was often circulated with them and they fit in pretty well. Bitrate: 128 kB/s
